{
  "id": "S2P05K23",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "ASSIGNING VALUES TO KEYS",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "help",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Terminal functions are used in SPF to perform cursor movement"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "and scrolling.  In most cases, terminal functions occur without"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Enter key processing, which means that they do not execute"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "any active primary or line commands.  Example terminal functions"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "include SCROLL-LEFT, CURSOR-DOWN, and ENTER-3270."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "To assign terminal functions to keys, the function name must"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "be surrounded by square brackets characters ('[' and ']')."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For example if the \"SCROLL-DOWN-MAX\" function were to be"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "assigned to the Ctrl-C key, you would change its value as"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "follows:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "NAME             VALUE"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Ctrl A+          :A"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Ctrl B+          BROWSE"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Ctrl C+          [SCROLL-DOWN-MAX]"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Once assigned, the editor will jump down to the bottom of the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "current edit session when encountering a Ctrl-C keystroke."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to continue)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
